=head1 DESCRIPTION

The access configuration information for the cluster.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 AuthenticationMode => Str

The desired authentication mode for the cluster. If you create a
cluster by using the EKS API, Amazon Web Services SDKs, or
CloudFormation, the default is C<CONFIG_MAP>. If you create the cluster
by using the Amazon Web Services Management Console, the default value
is C<API_AND_CONFIG_MAP>.


=head2 BootstrapClusterCreatorAdminPermissions => Bool

Specifies whether or not the cluster creator IAM principal was set as a
cluster admin access entry during cluster creation time. The default
value is C<true>.



